[[!meta title="Tails 2.0.1 is out"]]
[[!tag announce]]

This release fixes [[numerous security
issues|security/Numerous_security_holes_in_2.0]]. All users must
upgrade as soon as possible.

[[!toc levels=1]]

# Changes

## Upgrades and changes

- Upgrade Tor Browser to [5.5.2](https://blog.torproject.org/blog/tor-browser-552-released).

## Fixed problems

- Fix regression breaking boot on 32-bit UEFI platforms. ([[!tails_ticket 11007 desc="#11007"]])

# Known issues

See the current list of [[known issues|support/known_issues]].

# Download or upgrade

Go to the [[install]] or [[upgrade|doc/upgrade/]] page.

If your Tails does not
boot after an automatic upgrade, please [[upgrade your Tails
manually|doc/upgrade#manual]].

